  "name": "HCS_Segments_2016_2025",
  "type": "Feature Layer",
  "serviceItemId": "0a419966213d4945a9d5c417686448f0",
  "cacheMaxAge": 30,
  "displayField": "",
  "description": "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255); color:rgb(20,20,20); font-family:&amp;quot;Avenir Next&amp;quot;, Avenir, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size:16px;\"&gt;&lt;span style=\"display:inline !important; float:none; font-style:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:normal; text-align:start; text-decoration-color:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-indent:0px; text-transform:none; word-spacing:0px;\"&gt;This dashboard presents a comprehensive overview of Cleveland’s High Crash Segments from 2016 to 2025. High Crash Segments are defined as one-mile roadway sections where 10 or more serious injury or fatal crashes occurred within a five-year period. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255); color:rgb(74,74,74); font-family:&amp;quot;Avenir Next&amp;quot;, Avenir, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size:16px;\"&gt;&lt;span style=\"display:inline !important; float:none; font-style:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:normal; text-align:start; text-decoration-color:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-indent:0px; text-transform:none; word-spacing:0px;\"&gt;These segments highlight some of the most dangerous parts of the city’s street network.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Crash data is obtained from ODOT:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style=\"border:0px solid currentcolor; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(0, 97, 155); font-family:inherit; line-height:1.5; text-decoration:none;\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://gis.dot.state.oh.us/tims/CrashAnalytics/Login\"&gt;GCAT | ODOT TIMS (state.oh.us)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update Frequency&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255); color:rgb(74,74,74); font-family:inherit; font-size:16px;\"&gt;&lt;span style=\"border:0px solid currentcolor; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline !important; float:none; font-style:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:normal; line-height:1.5; text-align:start; text-decoration-color:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-indent:0px; text-transform:none; word-spacing:0px;\"&gt;Updated annually for the most recent 10-year period.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Contact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255); color:rgb(74,74,74); font-family:inherit; font-size:16px;\"&gt;&lt;span style=\"border:0px solid currentcolor; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline !important; float:none; font-style:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:normal; line-height:1.5; text-align:start; text-decoration-color:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-indent:0px; text-transform:none; word-spacing:0px;\"&gt;Cameron Roberts, Vision Zero Coordinator&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255); border:0px solid currentcolor; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(0, 97, 155); font-family:inherit; font-size:16px; font-style:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:normal; line-height:1.5; text-align:start; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0px; text-transform:none; word-spacing:0px;\" href=\"mailto:croberts5@clevelandohio.gov\" target=\"_blank\"&gt;croberts5@clevelandohio.gov&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
